'''David''' is one of Travis's past dates.

==History==
David was on a date with Travis when, while walking to the car, they heard a woman scream from inside her house. Travis told David to call 911 and then broke into the house, where he subdued the man who was beating his wife, allowing her to escape.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
He dated Travis before Travis was a firefighter.

==Notes and Trivia==
*On his date with Travis, he dressed as Janet from The Rocky Horror Picture Show.
